These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: poker, scrabble, canasta, domino, mah-jongg, billiard, go
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing poker and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person playing domino is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Game   | go | canasta | mah-jongg | poker | domino | scrabble | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, airplane, snowmobile, motorbike, ship, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the roller##2
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Transport   | scooter | tram | roller | snowmobile | motorbike | airplane | ship |

