.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
House: cottage, modern, colonial, cape-cod, ranch-style, wooden, craftsman
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the wooden house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the cottage house##1
4. the wooden house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
5. the modern house is on the left of the cottage house##1
6. the ranch-style house is between the wooden house and the modern house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| House   | craftsman | wooden | ranch-style | modern | cottage | colonial | cape-cod |

