.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, musical, satire, disaster, thriller, drama
1. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person watching drama movies is in the middle##1
7. the person watching musical movies is the person watching musical movies##1
8. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | martial-arts | satire | drama | disaster | crime | musical |

