.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip, balloon-flower, zinnia, iris, aconite, rose
1. the person who growsaconite is between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsiris##2
2. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
3. the person who growszinnia is the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growsiris and the person who growstulip##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |      4       |   5   |     6     |   7    |
| Flower   | rose | zinnia | aconite | iris | balloon-flower | tulip | poppy |

