.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, april, october, july, november, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |   3    |    4    |     5      |   6    |  7  |
| Birthday   | june | april | november | september | july | october | august |

 